room_title: Escape room "Lost in Space" by Catch-22 in Milwaukee
room_description:
You and your group are space travelers in the year 3020. While searching for new galaxies, your ship has run out of its energy source to continue on.

Luckily your crew was able to crash land, with minimum damage, on a nearby planet that supplies the energy source you seek.

You must repair your ship and find the much-needed energy source within 1 hour before the black hole needed to travel back home closes! Good luck!
